Package org.lukep.javavis.metrics

Interface Summary
IMeasurableNode Represents a single node that is able to have IMeasurableVisitors visit and apply metric measurements upon it.
IMeasurableVisitor A visitor to a measurable node in the object graph.
 

Class Summary
MeasurableVisitorPool Pools instances of IMeasurableVisitor for purposes of optimisation.
MetricAttribute Represents a static metric that is associated with an IMeasurableVisitor for measuring program models.
MetricMeasurement Represents an individual metric measurement.
MetricMeasurementRelation A relationship between two nodes in the abstract model graph.
MetricPreloader Helper class that pre-loads metric measurements to speed up the responsiveness of the user interface.
MetricRegistry The MetricRegistry is a singleton that stores all of the MetricAttributes and cached MetricMeasurements in the program's memory.
MetricThreshold The Class MetricThreshold.
MetricType The Class MetricType.
